                <aside class="toc-container">
                    <h3>On this page</h3>
                    <div class="toc">
                        <div class="toc">
<ul>
<li><a href="#the-alchemy-of-the-self">The Alchemy of the Self</a><ul>
<li><a href="#a-meditation-by-adept-emeritus-theron-of-the-silent-fulcrum">A Meditation by Adept-Emeritus Theron of the Silent Fulcrum</a></li>
